-- CADP (CONSTRUCTION AND ANALYSIS OF DISTRIBUTED PROCESSES)
-- http://cadp.inria.fr

This directory contains the following files:

 - bes.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the BES format
 - exp.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the EXP format
 - lnt.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the LNT language
 - lotos.lang:       GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the LOTOS language
 - mcl.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the MCL language
 - nupn.lang:        GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the NUPN format
 - rbc.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the RBC format
 - svl.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the SVL language
 - xtl.lang:         GtkSourceView 3.0 syntax mode for the XTL language

How to use these files:
-----------------------

Type the following shell commands:

	mkdir -p $HOME/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs
	ln -s $CADP/ext/gtk3/*.lang $HOME/.local/share/gtksourceview-3.0/language-specs

where $CADP is the pathname of the directory in which the CADP software
is installed on your machine.

